trans-unit.source: A ComponentRenameEventArgs provides data about a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename> event.
trans-unit.target: En ComponentRenameEventArgs inneholder data om en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename>hendelse.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentRename>

trans-unit.source: A ComponentRenameEventArgs object provides the following information: - A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A> property that references the component being renamed.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt for ComponentRenameEventArgs inneholder følgende informasjon: – en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A>egenskap som refererer til komponenten som gis nytt navn.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.Component%2A>

trans-unit.source: - An <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A> property that indicates the old name of the component.
trans-unit.target: – En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A>egenskap som angir det gamle navnet for komponenten.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.OldName%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A> property that indicates the new name of the component.
trans-unit.target: – En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A>egenskap som angir det nye navnet for komponenten.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs.NewName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentRenameEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.
